2 kids, PCOS, working mom. I prioritize myself. I focus on creating healthy habits. Movement, healthy diet, nothing too dramatic. I'm too close to an overweight BMI, it messes with my mind. But I can't go back, can't give up. I'll continue working on the inside until I feel better on the outside.

My biggest solo accomplishment has been a half marathon. Getting ready for a full, but have to mix in moving, building a house, kid starting kindergarten, and marriage. One day.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/hTML0Rd</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Monkeysboobsbutts]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Nothing to add</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/PuuGzWz</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/o1DNBCl.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/PuuGzWz</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[blank666man]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Fml</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/IgTWkyP</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/u0UIMYt.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/IgTWkyP</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[prisonmike1991]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>The Amazing Awoo Duo</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/iHLPKAU</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/tBkut2E.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/iHLPKAU</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[michaelv2]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>uh</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/tI58Q4U</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/QWEIb2T.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/tI58Q4U</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[AsshatTheCat]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Puppy day?</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/Wek3PYg</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/MFapamz.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/Wek3PYg</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Ultraruben]]></dc:creator>