><dc:creator><![CDATA[Rammsteinstochter]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Sometimes I forget Lord of the Rings was filmed 20 years ago</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/7xraHUZ</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Pxfuftz.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/7xraHUZ</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[LordofRivendell]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Zebras and Shadows</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/69Ta0lx</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/u3dbo8r.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/1kskreB.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>https://twitter.com/LarsJohanL/status/1505999058825097219?t=w8H98cYNho6TA9lCF2oUrw&s=19</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/69Ta0lx</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[querolasaberdisso]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Girl power</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/Fl9lyRo</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Yoz7c5U.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Most of my customers don't care who works on their computer or ask me IT questions all the time without assuming I'm a secretary. But at least once a day I get the "I need to talk to the guy" person who won't listen, isn't interested in hearing I am the tech, belittle me, or by god they need to hear what I said but in a man's voice.
I had four people ask for "the guy" today. I had to sit in the back for awhile to just.... Calm down/try not to cry. It's been bothering me more and more lately.
I've been a tech for 8 years. I work in the custom PC field. I'm not brilliant or anything but I know a few things and if I don't I'm not afraid to admit it and I can usually figure it out. I've had guys buy MY builds and gush about how great they are but give the guys the credit. I know I know, I'm screaming into the void.... I'm just so tired. I've worked for corporate and it was a nightmare there too, one manager told me "oh yeah we hired you because we had to hire a girl and you're the only one that applied"
Fuuuuuuuuuck. I already have low self esteem. I'm just tired. I want out. And my coworkers defend me up and down, I'm not in a toxic work environment by any means. They're happy to say "oh you need to ask her I have no idea" but these people keep coming and I'm sick of it. Kinda just want to be a hermit, live on a hill, make some frog friends, and make little biscuits and tea and read books. 
That's a field I can get into right?

Edit: thank you all for the outpouring of love and support I woke up to this morning. I have no idea what I want to be when I grow up, but I definitely have some thinking to do. You're all awesome.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/Fl9lyRo</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[mnstrqn]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Allow him to retort</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/SCVi0pm</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/DqG6rBI.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>https://twitter.com/__Chimaera/status/1503423951015456770</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/n6zK9WW.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>https://twitter.com/ElieNYC/status/1499381281603440641</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/LlxkOMl.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>https://twitter.com/ElieNYC/status/1500131620250128385</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/9GmmHIP.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>https://twitter.com/ElieNYC/status/1503419005863927808</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/SCVi0pm</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[springelmogizmo]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Wednesday at the club</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/OZFL6JQ</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/9eKUWW3.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/OZFL6JQ</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[funkystay]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>This is Jerry the golden retriever and he is just living his best life.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/zIGpAuf</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/yhTQZby.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Source : www.tiktok.com/@Jerry_thechicagodog</div></div>]]></