idth: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>This was the first attempt I had made at dating again after my last girlfriend punched me in the jaw because I asked if we could take a break.

I don't know what's wrong with me. I'm a 6'3" 31 year old guy, who doesn't drink smoke or do drugs. My passions are riding my bike, reading, cooking, and weightlifting. I'm also teaching myself how to tailor. And I'm built like a silverback gorilla. I do my best not to hide any of these qualities cuz I'm not ashamed of them.

Maybe I'm attracted to the wrong people for me. Maybe the system's broken for introverted folks like me. Maybe I'm not trying hard enough. Maybe... Maybe some people are just destined to be alone.

Tomorrow I'll get back to meal prepping, weightlifting, putting pockets on dresses, and posting dank memes on Imgur but Tonight I'm going to let myself be miserable.

Stay Classy Imgur.

Most Viral Edit: I set my phone down for a couple of our to eat an entire menus worth of desserts and come back to my DM full of Katniss Everdeens, suppose that what I get for mentioning the tailoring.

1) Thank you for the support.

2) I think I'm gonna take a knee and just workout alot til summer, this hit me harder than it should have.

3) All I've done so far with tailoring is make a couple of bad suits, and add a lot of pockets to existing dresses or make bigger pockets on jeans. It's kind of hard to be built like I am and convince a girl to come to his place, take her clothes off, get true measurements, and start discussing pattern and Materials without it seem like I'm trying to fuck/murder her.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/qr5l1es</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Beattywill80]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/TSs6ZS9</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/QnuOjXF.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/TSs6ZS9</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[mfrybeasley]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Good bye Eeyore.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/qNJbGhe</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/YP2lj9m.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I met you the day you were born. I was the first person you saw when your eyes opened. You were my first pup. That was 12 years and 9 months ago. You were my Eeyore. The one who greeted me when I got home. The one who annoyed me when I was lake feeding you.

You had a rough few months, and I was hoping you would let me know when it was time. Tonight you did. Thank you for all the memories and good times.

I will miss and never forget you bud.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/BNGrXXU.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Good bye my Eeyore. 6/26/09-3/22/22</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/qNJbGhe</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[jrredneck]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>One.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/eTosuwP</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/rK6Sjvv.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/eTosuwP</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[rayrevels]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Where shadows become the solid form and striped backs are lost in the light.. Zoom in</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/mn9h6AB</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/XZ6LHGM.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/mn9h6AB</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[BeniDune]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Daddy's good boy :)</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/yWWv7Lo</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/8tGxLQK.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Source : https://instagram.com/gainz_thegoodboy</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/yWWv7Lo</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Rammsteinstochter]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>You Can’t Handle the Truth</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/pYSkfME</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/yUoMXmK.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/pYSkfME</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[AustinKocher]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>They took on the media moguls and won!</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/gsMm6yQ</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i